text:
That was a real heart-to-heart 2wice date. You can see in Yeondub's eyes that this conversation was really meaningful to them.
I agree with Dahyun that Nayeon's personality plays a big part in why this group is so fun and close. 
Instead of playing rank as the oldest unnie, her playful ways and how she integrates herself pulled everyone closer. Nayeon seems to be especially close with 3mix, Momo and Chaeyoung and even though the others are younger, they can pull jokes at her without worry. At the same time she is very considerate like when she got the 1st solo in Twice, she worried about her members' feelings. When she works hard to the brink of exhaustion, she doesn't show her tiredness to not affect group activities.
I think that kind of consideration is a big part why Twice lasts longer than any other girl group.
